quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  20,106,"“Nitachilileka (litaka) lili chiŵata chetilisye tyatyatya!”"
  20,107,"“Ngasilliona palakwepo litiŵi namuno chikwesya.”"
  20,108,"Lyele lisikulyo tachinkuuya ŵanganyao nkuŵilanga (jwa Allah) mwangali kunsembenduka jwalakwejo, sano maloŵe ni gaachintulalila (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, ni ngasimpikana ikaŵeje kusongona ni misindo ja sajo."
  21,82,"Nambo soni m’mashetani mwaliji mwana ŵaŵaliji nkuntiŵilila (Sulaimanajo m’mbwani kuja kunsosela ngalekale), ni ŵaliji nkupanganya soni masengo gane gangaŵaga gele (mpela yakutaŵataŵa). Ni twaliji Uwwe tuli nkwalonda ŵanganyao."
  21,83,"Soni (munkumbuchilani) Ayyubu, ndema jajwaŵilasile Ambujegwe (pakwaŵenda) kuti: “Chisimu une gangwayiye masausyo, sano Mmwe ni Ŵachanasa channope kwapunda ŵachanasa wosope.”"
  21,84,"Basi ni twan’jitiche, ni twantyochesye masausyo gajwaliji nago, ni twampele ŵapeŵasa ŵakwe, ni konjechesya soni paŵanganyao ŵane ŵanti mpela ŵawowo, (twantendele yosope yeneyi kuŵa) ukoto wakuumila Kukwetu, ni (kuti chiŵe) chikumbusyo kwa akutenda ibada."
  22,58,"Sano aŵala ŵaŵasamile petala lya Allah, kaneko ni kuulajidwa kapena kuwa, chisimu Allah tachapa lisiki lyambone, soni chisimu Allah ni jwaali Jwambone nnope mwa akupeleka lisiki."
  22,59,"Chisimu ŵanganyao tachajinjisya pakwinjila patachipanonyela (ku Mbepo). Soni chisimu Allah ni Jwakumanyilila kusyesyene, Jwakutulala nnope ntima."
  22,60,"Yalakweyo ili iyyo. Sano juchauchisye ni ipotesi yakulandana ni ayila yajwapedwile jwalakwe kaneko ni kutendeledwa uwwanga, chisimu Allah tankamuchisye. Chisimu Allah ni Nkusiimaasya (ilemwa), Jwakuluka kusyene."
  23,34,"“Soni chisimu naga nkwika mwakun’jitika mundu mpela jenumanja, chisimu ŵanganyammwe pa jele ndemajo tim’be ŵakwasika.”"
  23,35,"“Ana akumpa chilanga chanti chisimu ŵanganyammwe patinchiwapo ni kusyuka litaka ni maupa, kuti chisimu jenumanja chinchikoposyedwa m’malembe?”"
  23,36,"“Ili kwanaula, ili kwanaula yankupedwa chilangayo (nganiiŵa itendekwe ata panandi).”"
  24,16,"Nambi uli soni pandema jamwajipikene (abaliji) nganim’becheta kuti: “Ngaikuŵa yakuŵajilwa kukwetu kuti tuŵecheteje yalakweyi, kuswejela ni Kwenu (Mmwe Ambuje)! Awu ni unami wekulungwa nnope.”"
  24,17,"Allah akun’jamuka kuti ngasim’bujauja soni kutenda yanti mpela yele mpaka kalakala nam’baga jenumanja n’di ŵakulupilila (kusyene)."
  24,18,"Soni Allah akusalichisya kukwenu ma Ȃya, soni Allah ni Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwalunda lwakusokoka."